y_post has_vote_column has_replies is_reply" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:8025480,&quot;user_id&quot;:4211218}"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fant-san.itch.io%2Fvillainotome" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" role="img" height="20" version="1.1" viewbox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fant-san.itch.io%2Fvillainotome" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" role="img" height="20" version="1.1" viewbox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/ant-san"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzYzNzk2MDgucG5n/25x25%23/xE86K4.png)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/ant-san">Anta</a></span><span class="post_date" title="2023-06-27 21:27:01"><a href="https://itch.io/post/8025480">2 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Due to spoilery plot reasons, a non-romance-good end is unlikely🤔<br></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" class="post_action reply_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fant-san.itch.io%2Fvillainotome">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies"><div id="post-8026974" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:8026974,&quot;user_id&quot;:1403386}"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fant-san.itch.io%2Fvillainotome" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_up" role="img" height="20" version="1.1" viewbox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fant-san.itch.io%2Fvillainotome" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" class="svgicon icon_vote_down" role="img" height="20" version="1.1" viewbox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/anithingavailable"><div class="post_avatar" style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-cyan.png)"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/anithingavailable">anithingavailable</a></span><span class="post_date" title="2023-06-28 07:27:17"><a href="https://itch.io/post/8026974">2 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body user_formatted" dir="auto"><p>Those are the best kinds of reasons =))</p><p>I feel like your games do a great job at creating tridimensional characters, so I can&#x27;t wait to get more drawn into the interactions with the LIs.<br></p><p><strong>Good luck with the development!!</strong><br></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" class="post_action reply_btn" href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fant-san.itch.io%2Fvillainotome">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="post-8023041" class="community_post has_vote_column has_replies" data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:8023041,&quot;user_id&quot;:5190326}"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=h